This MODEL DRIVER implementation of the INN model computes energy, forces, and virial using the CLUSTER, NEIGH_PURE_F, or MI_OPBC_F NBC methods.

-----------------------------------------
A note on how this model is implemented:


The publication can be found at:

     Berk Onat, Ekin D. Cubuk, Brad D. Malone, and Efthimios Kaxiras, "Implanted neural network potentials: Application to Li-Si alloys", Phys. Rev. B 97, 094106

Written by Berk Onat (2014-2016 Harvard University). Current contact email: bonat@warwick.ac.uk

